CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FA man who sparked a terror alert by
OL,7,Fleaving a fake stick of dynamite
OL,8,Foutside the headquarters of MI5 will
OL,9,Fbe sentenced today.
OL,11,FBrazilian national Julian Valente
OL,12,FPereira, 32, staged a protest at the
OL,13,Fsecret services base at Thames House,
OL,14,Fin central London, a day after finding
OL,15,Fout his asylum claim had been rejected.
OL,17,FCCTV footage shows Pereira stuffing
OL,18,Fpaperwork about his immigration case
OL,19,Fthrough the doors of the building,
OL,20,Fbefore retrieving the "dynamite" from
OL,21,Fhis bag.
OL,26,@|D@WOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FHe initially threw the object to the
OL,7,Fpavement, allowing the CCTV operator
OL,8,Fto zoom in to reveal what appeared to
OL,9,Fbe a fuse hanging out of the top of
OL,10,Fthe brown cylinder.
OL,12,FPereira is then seen moving the
OL,13,Fobject, propping it up against the MI5
OL,14,FHQ doors, with a green cigarette
OL,15,Flighter positioned nearby.
OL,17,FA counter terrorism bomb expert was
OL,18,Fcalled in, and it was then discovered
OL,19,FPereira had used rolled-up A4 paper,
OL,20,Fbrown masking tape, and string to
OL,21,Fcreate the fake dynamite.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FThe incident happened on January 1,
OL,7,Fthe day after Pereira's final appeal
OL,8,Ffor asylum had been dismissed by a
OL,9,Fjudge.
OL,11,FAfter a trial at City of London
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court, Chief Magistrate
OL,13,FPaul Goldspring found Pereira guilty
OL,14,Fof carrying out a bomb hoax,
OL,15,Fconcluding he had wanted those
OL,16,Fwatching to believe the device was
OL,17,Freal.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FPereira has been remanded into custody
OL,7,Funtil sentencing on April 1, and the
OL,8,Ffootage of the incident has now been
OL,9,Freleased by the Crown Prosecution
OL,10,FService.
OL,12,FProsecutor Shannon Revel told the
OL,13,Ftrial Pereira has admitted he wanted
OL,14,F"maximum attention" on his complaints
OL,15,Fagainst the Home Office, after a long-
OL,16,Frunning failed bid for asylum.
OL,18,F"No-one was going to pay attention to
OL,19,Fthis act if they thought it was
OL,20,Fmasking tape and paper," she said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@SO]zD@AOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,F"The attention he desperately wanted
OL,7,Fon January 1 is only achieved by the
OL,8,Ffact that someone believed that object
OL,9,Fcould explode."
OL,11,FPereira came to the UK with permission
OL,12,Fto work in July 2018 and has remained
OL,13,Fin the country illegally since
OL,14,FFebruary 2019.
OL,16,F"The defendant attended Thames House
OL,17,Fin Millbank, knowing it to be the
OL,18,Fheadquarters of the security services
OL,19,FMI5," said Ms Revel.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@OO]xD@AOU{D@EO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,F"He tried to open the doors of the
OL,7,Fbuilding without success.
OL,9,F"He started to push pieces of paper
OL,10,Fbetween the closed doors that were
OL,11,Flocked.
OL,13,F"He took an item fashioned from paper,
OL,14,Fstring and masking tape out of his
OL,15,Fjacket pocket.
OL,17,F"The object was designed to look like
OL,18,Fa stick of dynamite."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FGiving evidence, Pereira said he left
OL,7,Fthe object at the front of MI5 because
OL,8,Fhe wanted to "catch the attention" of
OL,9,Fthe security services.
OL,11,F"I swear it wasn't my intention to
OL,12,Fcause any disruption on Vauxhall
OL,13,FBridge," he said.
OL,15,FHe told the court he had also visited
OL,16,FBuckingham Palace to throw a bag
OL,17,Fcontaining a copy of the immigration
OL,18,Fruling and a knife stabbed through his
OL,19,FID inside the perimeter gates.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@bO]sD@AOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FIn messages read out during the trial,
OL,7,FPereira had told a friend of his plan.
OL,9,F"I'm going to Buckingham Palace with a
OL,10,Fknife and one pen drive," he wrote,
OL,11,Fadding: "All the information is inside
OL,12,Fthe pen drive."
OL,14,FWhen he was told to "stop being an
OL,15,Fidiot", Pereira wrote: "I'm going to
OL,16,Ftry and get attention.
OL,18,F"I'm going to throw the bag into
OL,19,FBuckingham Palace."
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@YO]sD@IOUtD@OO]vD@UOUwD@FO]wD@
OL,26,AXOUzD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
