OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FIn a note on his phone from August
OL,7,F2025, Pereira wrote about "MI5
OL,8,Fterrorising people inside hotels", and
OL,9,Fadded: "I need to see the King."
OL,11,FHe also said he planned to "give
OL,12,Finformation" to the Archbishop of
OL,13,FCanterbury as a precaution.
OL,15,FWhen giving evidence, Pereira insisted
OL,16,Fthe device he left outside MI5 would
OL,17,Fnot have been mistaken for an
OL,18,Fexplosive, but added: "The news inside
OL,19,Fwas dynamite."
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@aO]qD@HOUqD@`O]sD@\OUtD@LO]zD@
OL,26,AWOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
