OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FPereira was arrested in his room at an
OL,7,Fasylum hotel in Uxbridge, west London,
OL,8,Fand told officers about his "long and
OL,9,Ftireless battle with the Home Office
OL,10,Fto try to attain asylum", said the
OL,11,Fprosecutor.
OL,13,FThe court heard that Pereira made
OL,14,Fallegations of Home Office
OL,15,F"corruption", claimed illegal
OL,16,Fimmigrants are employed by the
OL,17,FGovernment department, and said those
OL,18,Fin the system are living in "squalor".
OL,26,@pD@]OUrD@XO]wD@AOUwD@LO]zD@]OUzD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FJudge Goldspring was also told that
OL,7,FPereira handed himself in to police as
OL,8,Fan overstayer in October 2020, but
OL,9,Flater sought asylum after being told
OL,10,Fto leave the UK.
OL,12,FHe was placed in asylum seeker
OL,13,Faccommodation in June 2021, asylum was
OL,14,Frefused in 2023, and his appeal
OL,15,Fagainst that decision was rejected by
OL,16,Fa judge on December 31 2025.
OL,18,FThe court heard that Pereira's paid-
OL,19,Ffor accommodation was withdrawn on
OL,20,FJanuary 9.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775063147
OL,3,CMan who sparked bomb hoax with fake
OL,4,Cdynamite outside MI5 to be sentenced
OL,6,FIn his police interview, he told
OL,7,Fofficers he has schizophrenia and had
OL,8,Fbeen hearing voices in his head.
OL,10,FHe denied carrying out a bomb hoax by
OL,11,Fplacing an article with intent.
OL,13,FThe judge asked for reports on
OL,14,FPereira's mental health and risk of
OL,15,Freoffending, and warned that he may be
OL,16,Fjailed or sent to the Crown Court for
OL,17,Fsentencing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
